treeExplanation.short: Emphasises the durability of the Bear Form.
treeExplanation.long: Relying on the bear form, this line bolsters personal defences while weakening the enemy.

treeInfo: Upon taking damage in Man form (20% chance in bear form):
This effect can only occur once every 8 seconds.

tooltipExplanation: Calculated and precise, your attacks hit their mark while bolstering your defences against any retaliation.
The mitigation buff stacks up to 5 times.
passiv.tooltipDamage: (230 + 2.3 * Melee Offence)% of Main-hand + bonus Damage
